---
title: Pork Sausage Spaghetti alla Positano with Tomato, Zucchini, and Lemon
description: Does your love for pasta know no bounds? We’ve got the perfect recipe for any self-professed carb connoisseur. Crispy pork sausage, tender bites of zucchini, jammy tomato, and a lemon-spiked garlic herb sauce are tossed with spaghetti for a dish that’s hearty, satisfying, and comforting. A sprinkle of Parmesan and chili flakes take the dish to new heights of bellissimo.
